{"tid":884454,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[港女] 點解女人可以咁雙重標準","createTime":"2018-10-31T15:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T15:52:30.000Z","uid":107184,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1b196fcac8a66f9441481725ef9385d6f3032582","tid":884454,"uid":107184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T15:00:02.000Z","msg":"永遠9成既野都係男人做得女人唔做得<br />\n你做左就好似犯下彌天大禍 又話你唔愛我啦個d<br />\n佢做就永遠無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如 你同佢㩒一陣電話 比佢屌到飛起<br />\n佢係咁以撞到下講一句痛就expect你放低哂手頭上既野去哄佢<br />\n調翻轉 佢同你出街㩒電話 㩒撚到唔撚so你叫你咪撚煩佢不特止 仲話撚之你撞到斷手跌斷腳 唔會問候你半句<br />\n最撚搞笑事後仲屌9你做咩嬲部電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有次次鬧交 事後話想同你討論翻個問題 原來淨係想聽你講自己做錯咩 我講左一句話可能大家性格都係硬頸 佢可以ff到話我淨係話佢唔岩 我真係無言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外生活有太多例子 未能一一列舉出黎<br />\n仲未計佢平時d難聽說話 嫌我窮嫌我矮嫌我呢樣個樣 又話可以揀個更好 會同第二條仔出街個d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底係我條女先係咁港女 定係香港所有女仔都係高高再上 男人就賤過地底泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5421ed6adfc1327953e89aa434f07f1edfdd967","tid":884454,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T15:04:16.000Z","msg":"g"},{"pid":"568f29259d2048b54e4c2cfcf46960a7b0ca7c89","tid":884454,"uid":218575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T15:05:09.000Z","msg":"分手"},{"pid":"37106861b77c98614274d017acc967070a76d1e8","tid":884454,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T15:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/31/230603_417c1ac791039bdc3077e8d0f57dbf4c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F31%2F230603_417c1ac791039bdc3077e8d0f57dbf4c.gif&h=9e274279&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5e24a04c669a78b64f3c0ce0e067a59092da258","tid":884454,"uid":107184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q